column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,  p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,p.PetroR9#_u, p.PetroR9#_g,p.PetroR9#_r,p.PetroR9#_i,p.PetroR9#_z, p.PetroR5#_u,p.PetroR5#_g,p.PetroR5#_r,p.PetroR5#_i,p.PetroR5#_z,  s.class, s.z as redshift FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN galSpecExtra AS gs ON gs.specObjID = s.specObjID WHERE   s.class = &&&  AND s.z BETWEEN # AND #
